            </item>
          </list>
        </para>
      </explnote.group>
      <explnote.group>
        <heading>Clause by clause analysis</heading>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 1</emphasis> states the Bill's title.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 2</emphasis> provides for the Bill's commencement.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clauses 3 to 6</emphasis> deal with preliminary matters, including the Bill's purpose.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clauses 7 to 14</emphasis> enable Maniapoto to make decisions about the Waipa River. The tools provided are the vision and strategy (set out in <emphasis style="italic">Schedule 1</emphasis>), membership of the river authority, and the making of an Upper Waipa River integrated management plan.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clauses 15 to 31</emphasis> deal with the Maniapoto Iwi Environmental Management Plan and enable Maniapoto to enter a joint management agreement with local authorities.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clauses 32 to 35</emphasis> deal with miscellaneous matters.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 36</emphasis> provides the process for extending the vision and strategy to the Upper Waipa River.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Schedule 1</emphasis> contains the vision and strategy.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
        <clause.desc>
          <para>
            <text><emphasis style="italic">Schedule 2</emphasis> describes the process for making and updating the Upper Waipa River integrated management plan.</text>
          </para>
        </clause.desc>
      </explnote.group>
    </explnote>
